ing the ODE model. We study these\nPDEs and obtain their solutions, obtaining for the framework of PDEs some of\nthe classical results, like existence of polynomial solutions (Laguerre,\nHermite and Chebyshev polynomials).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2019 23:40:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-08"}
